в•‘               SCIENTIFIC SUMMARY & BIOLOGICAL INTERPRETATION                в•‘
в•љв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ќ

WHAT THIS MODEL CAPTURES (grounded in uploaded papers):
в”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ
1. PHOTOPHORETIC PROPULSION (Papers 1 & 4):
   vв‚Ђ в€ќ F_ph/Оі_drag в€ќ I_local  [Koss 2022, Eq. 1; Krauss 2006, Eq. 1]
   In shadow: vв‚Ђ в†’ 0 (stall). In light: vв‚Ђ = v_max.
   Physical scale: for 5 Вµm Pt-JP at 100 mW laser, vв‚Ђ ~ 10вЂ“100 Вµm/s.

2. ROTATIONAL DIFFUSION (Paper 2):
   D_r = О·ВІ/2 = k_BT/(8ПЂО·_fluidВ·aВі)  [Lisin 2021, Eq. 1]
   Persistence length: L_p = vв‚Ђ/D_r  [Lisin 2021, Eq. 7]
   Physical scale: D_r ~ 0.01вЂ“10 sвЃ»В№ for 1вЂ“5 Вµm particles in water.

3. CIRCLE SWIMMING (Paper 3):
   Body-fixed torque from asymmetric Pt-cap creates intrinsic spin.
   Trajectory type depends on П‰_self/П‰_circling ratio:
     П‰_self/П‰ = 1 в†’ circular;   n в†’ epitrochoidal  [Nosenko 2020, Sec. IV]

4. COLLECTIVE ALIGNMENT (Vicsek-type):
   J couples particle orientations within radius R_align.
   Physical mechanism: combined thermal radiation + thermoosmotic coupling.
   Phase boundary: О·_c в€ќ в€љ(JВ·ПЃВ·RВІ)  [Vicsek 1995, extended in Paper 2]

5. SHADOWING & COLLECTIVE RESCUE:
   Geometric shadow stalls isolated particles (Paper 1).
   Swarm radiation from bright neighbours rescues shadowed particles.
   This is a NEW EMERGENT BEHAVIOUR not present in single-particle physics.

HONEST LIMITATIONS:
в”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ
вњ— Dry active matter: no hydrodynamic interactions (Stokes flow neglected).
  Real impact: ~20вЂ“40% error in alignment coupling magnitude.
вњ— Overdamped only: inertial delay number ОІ = ОЅ/П‰ >> 1 assumed.
  Valid for ОІ >> 1 (colloidal particles in liquid). Not valid for plasma JP.
  Plasma JPs have ОІ ~ 0.1вЂ“10 в†’ inertial effects matter (Paper 2, Paper 3)!
вњ— Geometric optics: no wave optics, diffraction, or scattering in shadow.
вњ— No particle-size polydispersity: real JP batches have ~5вЂ“10% size variation.
вњ— 2D only: real experiments are quasi-2D with out-of-plane fluctuations.
вњ— Phenomenological J: true physical coupling involves both radiation
  AND thermoosmotic flows вЂ” our J merges these into one constant.

MAPPING TO REAL BIOLOGY:
в”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ
вЂў J (alignment)  ~ quorum-sensing coupling in bacteria (Pseudomonas, E. coli)
вЂў О± (phototaxis) ~ chemotaxis gradient response (camp signalling)
вЂў Shadow          ~ physical barrier in biofilm formation / drug delivery
вЂў Swarm delivery  ~ targeted nanoparticle delivery past biological barriers
вЂў Phase diagram   ~ orderвЂ“disorder transition in bacterial collective motion
  (Vicsek universality class, confirmed in Bacillus subtilis suspensions)

